      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nigerian-bank-stocks-rise-shrugging-off-tough-new-capital-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚银行对央行将资本金要求提高 10 倍不以为然，并表示该行业有足够的时间来适应。]]></description>
