      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/german-inflation-slows-further-as-ecb-readies-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国通胀 3 月份连续第三个月放缓，支撑了欧洲央行将于 6 月份开始降息的预期。]]></description>
